			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1. Load SCL and set up the tiefling path using the debug book.&#xD;&#xA;2. Recruit Karlach as an avatar.&#xD;&#xA;3. In recon: goto -54; 27; 140&#xD;&#xA;4. Speak with Mattis.&#xD;&#xA;OR&#xD;&#xA;1. Load SCL and set up the tiefling path using the debug book.&#xD;&#xA;2. Recruit Karlach&#xD;&#xA;3. In recon: goto -54; 27; 140&#xD;&#xA;4. Talk to Mattis as Karlach while she is far from the party." />
